      "en": {
        "content": "The question contains STATEMENT - 1 (Assertion) and STATEMENT - 2 (Reason) and has 4 choices (a), (b), (c) and (d) out of which ONLY ONE is correct.<br>\n<b>STATEMENT - 1</b> Alkali metals dissolve in liquid ammonia to give blue solutions. because<br>\n<b>STATEMENT - 2</b> Alkali metals is liquid ammonia give solvated species of the type [M(NH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>n</sub>]<sup>+</sup> (M =  alkali metals)",
